trans-unit.source: Provides for compilation and caching of queries for reuse.
trans-unit.target: 提供查詢的編譯和快取以供重複使用。

trans-unit.source: Conceptually this class contains a single method (`Compile`) with several overloads.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別包含單一方法的概念 (`Compile`) 數個多載。

trans-unit.source: You call the <xref:System.Data.Linq.CompiledQuery.Compile%2A> method to create a new delegate to represent the compiled query.

trans-unit.source: Compilation does not occur until the first time the query is executed.
